sentences: Terje Vik Schei (born 7 July 1974), better known by his stage name Tchort, is a Norwegian musician.
He was arrested in the early/mid nineties for assault and was in prison for 2 years.
Tchort with fellow Green Carnation performer Kjetil Nordhus, established his own record label, Sublife Productions in Kristiansand, Norway, on 1 July 2005.
The company is also turning its eye to cover design, and has stated that "various artists will present their work on Sublifeproductions.com in the near future"
